text: Nassarius fischeri is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Nassariidae, the Nassa mud snails or dog whelks. ==Distribution== This species occurs in the Atlantic Ocean off Angola. ==References== * Dautzenberg P. (1912). Mission Gruvel sur la côte occidentale d'Afrique (1909–1910): Mollusques marins.
